    ai_welcome: "👋 Hey! I'm the OrcaAppBuilder AI — ask me anything about building on Lightchain. Not sure where to start? Try asking:\n\n• \"What kind of app should I build?\"\n• \"How do I add AI to my app?\"\n• \"How do I share my app with friends?\"",
